name: WebMii
description: People search and company search engine
overview:
WebMii is people search and company search engine.

Controlling our digital identity is a main issue. What are the information displayed about myself on the web? How to obtain a full vision of what’s about me (and the others) on the web?

WebMii is a people search mash up that centralizes public information from other websites. For each search, WebMii shows the source of the presented information. WebMii aims to allow people to better know and control the information displayed about themselves on the web.

WebMii give a much more accurate, full and clear vision of what’s online about someone than its competitors. WebMii show the PeopleRank of a person: the PeopleRank is the on line visibility score for someone. It is calculated by WebMii according to anyone visibility on the web.

WebMii also allows to search for companies, brands ans products. It then displays their BrandRank.
